MasterChef UK - Series 12, Episode 8




Five more amateurs try to prove to judges John Torode and Gregg Wallace that they have the potential to be the 2016 MasterChef Champion. In this heat, the contestants must attempt to impress three MasterChef champions: 2005 champion Thomasina Miers, 2006 champion Peter Bayless and 2007 champion Steven Wallis.




Original Air Date: 07-Apr-2016
